{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1267,"text":"Before March, 2011, I was a photographic retoucher"},{"time":5321,"text":"based in New York City."},{"time":8268,"text":"We're pale, gray creatures."},{"time":10324,"text":"We hide in dark, windowless rooms,"},{"time":12384,"text":"and generally avoid sunlight."},{"time":14712,"text":"We make skinny models skinnier, perfect skin more perfect,"},{"time":18976,"text":"and the impossible possible,"},{"time":20956,"text":"and we get criticized in the press all the time,"},{"time":25006,"text":"but some of us are actually talented artists"},{"time":28507,"text":"with years of experience"},{"time":30587,"text":"and a real appreciation for images and photography."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34491,"text":"On March 11, 2011, I watched from home, as the rest"},{"time":39655,"text":"of the world did, as the tragic events unfolded in Japan."},{"time":43491,"text":"Soon after, an organization I volunteer with,"},{"time":45664,"text":"All Hands Volunteers, were on the ground, within days,"},{"time":49506,"text":"working as part of the response efforts."},{"time":52338,"text":"I, along with hundreds of other volunteers,"},{"time":54634,"text":"knew we couldn't just sit at home,"},{"time":56298,"text":"so I decided to join them for three weeks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60022,"text":"On May the 13th, I made my way to the town of ÅŒfunato."},{"time":63667,"text":"It's a small fishing town in Iwate Prefecture,"},{"time":67347,"text":"about 50,000 people,"},{"time":69754,"text":"one of the first that was hit by the wave."},{"time":72559,"text":"The waters here have been recorded at reaching"},{"time":75370,"text":"over 24 meters in height,"},{"time":78072,"text":"and traveled over two miles inland."},{"time":79781,"text":"As you can imagine, the town had been devastated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83323,"text":"We pulled debris from canals and ditches."},{"time":85854,"text":"We cleaned schools. We de-mudded and gutted homes"},{"time":89285,"text":"ready for renovation and rehabilitation."},{"time":91783,"text":"We cleared tons and tons of stinking, rotting fish carcasses"},{"time":96235,"text":"from the local fish processing plant."},{"time":98454,"text":"We got dirty, and we loved it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101863,"text":"For weeks, all the volunteers and locals alike"},{"time":104980,"text":"had been finding similar things."},{"time":107220,"text":"They'd been finding photos and photo albums"},{"time":110166,"text":"and cameras and SD cards."},{"time":112799,"text":"And everyone was doing the same."},{"time":114015,"text":"They were collecting them up, and handing them in to"},{"time":116680,"text":"various places around the different towns for safekeeping."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119853,"text":"Now, it wasn't until this point that I realized"},{"time":122969,"text":"that these photos were such a huge part"},{"time":125399,"text":"of the personal loss these people had felt."},{"time":128399,"text":"As they had run from the wave, and for their lives,"},{"time":131193,"text":"absolutely everything they had,"},{"time":133713,"text":"everything had to be left behind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136537,"text":"At the end of my first week there, I found myself"},{"time":138822,"text":"helping out in an evacuation center in the town."},{"time":142016,"text":"I was helping clean the onsen, the communal onsen,"},{"time":145351,"text":"the huge giant bathtubs."},{"time":147657,"text":"This happened to also be a place in the town where"},{"time":150094,"text":"the evacuation center was collecting the photos."},{"time":153098,"text":"This is where people were handing them in,"},{"time":155023,"text":"and I was honored that day that they actually trusted me"},{"time":157531,"text":"to help them start hand-cleaning them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160175,"text":"Now, it was emotional and it was inspiring,"},{"time":163224,"text":"and I've always heard about thinking outside the box,"},{"time":166982,"text":"but it wasn't until I had actually gotten outside of my box"},{"time":170393,"text":"that something happened."},{"time":172820,"text":"As I looked through the photos, there were some"},{"time":174873,"text":"were over a hundred years old,"},{"time":176639,"text":"some still in the envelope from the processing lab,"},{"time":180223,"text":"I couldn't help but think as a retoucher"},{"time":182113,"text":"that I could fix that tear and mend that scratch,"},{"time":184938,"text":"and I knew hundreds of people who could do the same."},{"time":188975,"text":"So that evening, I just reached out on Facebook"},{"time":191362,"text":"and asked a few of them, and by morning"},{"time":193556,"text":"the response had been so overwhelming and so positive,"},{"time":197035,"text":"I knew we had to give it a go."},{"time":198900,"text":"So we started retouching photos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201754,"text":"This was the very first."},{"time":204547,"text":"Not terribly damaged, but where the water had caused"},{"time":209154,"text":"that discoloration on the girl's face"},{"time":211340,"text":"had to be repaired with such accuracy and delicacy."},{"time":214943,"text":"Otherwise, that little girl isn't going to look"},{"time":217238,"text":"like that little girl anymore, and surely that's as tragic"},{"time":219938,"text":"as having the photo damaged."},{"time":223482,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229810,"text":"Over time, more photos came in, thankfully,"},{"time":233023,"text":"and more retouchers were needed,"},{"time":236497,"text":"and so I reached out again on Facebook and LinkedIn,"},{"time":239435,"text":"and within five days, 80 people wanted to help"},{"time":242518,"text":"from 12 different countries."},{"time":244487,"text":"Within two weeks, I had 150 people"},{"time":246856,"text":"wanting to join in."},{"time":248727,"text":"Within Japan, by July, we'd branched out"},{"time":251103,"text":"to the neighboring town of Rikuzentakata,"},{"time":253715,"text":"further north to a town called Yamada."},{"time":256109,"text":"Once a week, we would set up our scanning equipment"},{"time":259377,"text":"in the temporary photo libraries that had been set up,"},{"time":261885,"text":"where people were reclaiming their photos."},{"time":264258,"text":"The older ladies sometimes hadn't seen a scanner before,"},{"time":268090,"text":"but within 10 minutes of them finding their lost photo,"},{"time":271964,"text":"they could give it to us, have it scanned,"},{"time":273873,"text":"uploaded to a cloud server, it would be downloaded"},{"time":275887,"text":"by a gaijin, a stranger,"},{"time":278520,"text":"somewhere on the other side of the globe,"},{"time":280623,"text":"and it'd start being fixed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282987,"text":"The time it took, however, to get it back"},{"time":286125,"text":"is a completely different story,"},{"time":288172,"text":"and it depended obviously on the damage involved."},{"time":290760,"text":"It could take an hour. It could take weeks."},{"time":292493,"text":"It could take months."},{"time":294597,"text":"The kimono in this shot pretty much had to be hand-drawn,"},{"time":298714,"text":"or pieced together, picking out the remaining parts of color"},{"time":302416,"text":"and detail that the water hadn't damaged."},{"time":304846,"text":"It was very time-consuming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307591,"text":"Now, all these photos had been damaged by water,"},{"time":310212,"text":"submerged in salt water, covered in bacteria,"},{"time":313543,"text":"in sewage, sometimes even in oil, all of which over time"},{"time":316984,"text":"is going to continue to damage them,"},{"time":318928,"text":"so hand-cleaning them was a huge part of the project."},{"time":322044,"text":"We couldn't retouch the photo unless it was cleaned,"},{"time":325014,"text":"dry and reclaimed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328030,"text":"Now, we were lucky with our hand-cleaning."},{"time":330482,"text":"We had an amazing local woman who guided us."},{"time":333719,"text":"It's very easy to do more damage to those damaged photos."},{"time":337912,"text":"As my team leader Wynne once said,"},{"time":339697,"text":"it's like doing a tattoo on someone."},{"time":341643,"text":"You don't get a chance to mess it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345174,"text":"The lady who brought us these photos was lucky,"},{"time":348157,"text":"as far as the photos go."},{"time":350387,"text":"She had started hand-cleaning them herself and stopped"},{"time":352769,"text":"when she realized she was doing more damage."},{"time":355188,"text":"She also had duplicates."},{"time":357439,"text":"Areas like her husband and her face, which otherwise"},{"time":360532,"text":"would have been completely impossible to fix,"},{"time":362636,"text":"we could just put them together in one good photo,"},{"time":365494,"text":"and remake the whole photo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367946,"text":"When she collected the photos from us,"},{"time":370624,"text":"she shared a bit of her story with us."},{"time":372987,"text":"Her photos were found by her husband's colleagues"},{"time":375947,"text":"at a local fire department in the debris"},{"time":377937,"text":"a long way from where the home had once stood,"},{"time":381053,"text":"and they'd recognized him."},{"time":383228,"text":"The day of the tsunami, he'd actually been in charge"},{"time":385509,"text":"of making sure the tsunami gates were closed."},{"time":388036,"text":"He had to go towards the water as the sirens sounded."},{"time":391164,"text":"Her two little boys, not so little anymore, but her two boys"},{"time":394606,"text":"were both at school, separate schools."},{"time":396796,"text":"One of them got caught up in the water."},{"time":399364,"text":"It took her a week to find them all again"},{"time":401311,"text":"and find out that they had all survived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403708,"text":"The day I gave her the photos also happened to be"},{"time":406638,"text":"her youngest son's 14th birthday."},{"time":410581,"text":"For her, despite all of this, those photos"},{"time":414254,"text":"were the perfect gift back to him,"},{"time":416965,"text":"something he could look at again, something he remembered from before"},{"time":420070,"text":"that wasn't still scarred from that day in March"},{"time":424328,"text":"when absolutely everything else in his life had changed"},{"time":427143,"text":"or been destroyed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431292,"text":"After six months in Japan,"},{"time":433149,"text":"1,100 volunteers had passed through All Hands,"},{"time":436299,"text":"hundreds of whom had helped us hand-clean"},{"time":438549,"text":"over 135,000 photographs,"},{"time":441789,"text":"the large majority â€” (Applause) â€”"},{"time":447493,"text":"a large majority of which did actually find their home again,"},{"time":450723,"text":"importantly."},{"time":453478,"text":"Over five hundred volunteers around the globe"},{"time":456651,"text":"helped us get 90 families hundreds of photographs back,"},{"time":461309,"text":"fully restored and retouched."},{"time":463559,"text":"During this time, we hadn't really spent more than"},{"time":466012,"text":"about a thousand dollars in equipment and materials,"},{"time":468858,"text":"most of which was printer inks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472188,"text":"We take photos constantly."},{"time":475075,"text":"A photo is a reminder of someone or something,"},{"time":477644,"text":"a place, a relationship, a loved one."},{"time":480502,"text":"They're our memory-keepers and our histories,"},{"time":483011,"text":"the last thing we would grab"},{"time":485723,"text":"and the first thing you'd go back to look for."},{"time":488231,"text":"That's all this project was about,"},{"time":490335,"text":"about restoring those little bits of humanity,"},{"time":493766,"text":"giving someone that connection back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495878,"text":"When a photo like this can be returned to someone like this,"},{"time":501571,"text":"it makes a huge difference"},{"time":503655,"text":"in the lives of the person receiving it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506440,"text":"The project's also made a big difference in the lives of the retouchers."},{"time":510243,"text":"For some of them, it's given them a connection"},{"time":513314,"text":"to something bigger, giving something back,"},{"time":515846,"text":"using their talents on something"},{"time":517725,"text":"other than skinny models and perfect skin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521145,"text":"I would like to conclude by reading an email"},{"time":523758,"text":"I got from one of them, Cindy,"},{"time":526188,"text":"the day I finally got back from Japan after six months."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530790,"text":"\"As I worked, I couldn't help but think about the individuals"},{"time":534545,"text":"and the stories represented in the images."},{"time":537694,"text":"One in particular, a photo of women of all ages,"},{"time":541181,"text":"from grandmother to little girl, gathered around a baby,"},{"time":545557,"text":"struck a chord, because a similar photo from my family,"},{"time":549079,"text":"my grandmother and mother, myself,"},{"time":551531,"text":"and newborn daughter, hangs on our wall."},{"time":554940,"text":"Across the globe, throughout the ages,"},{"time":558094,"text":"our basic needs are just the same, aren't they?\""},{"time":561983,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":564300,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}